## Step 0 Validation

This is a comprehensive check of all components. If you verified each section
as you went, most of these should already pass. Run through them to confirm
nothing was missed or broken by subsequent steps.

Run `tests/step0.sh` for automated checks, or verify manually below.

### V0.1 — Management Network

Ping every node and the NAS from your workstation:

```bash
{%- for node in nodes %}
ping -c 1 {{ node.mgmt_ip }}   # {{ node.name }}
{%- endfor %}
ping -c 1 {{ nas.ip }}          # NAS ({{ nas.hostname }})
```

- [ ] All {{ nodes | length }} nodes respond to ping
- [ ] NAS responds to ping

