### Port 53 Forwarding (WAN:53 → VM:8053)
- [ ] Verify port forwarding rules exist in Policy Engine → Port Forwarding:
      `DNS-forward-tcp` and `DNS-forward-udp` (or a single "Both" rule)
      WAN Port: `53`, Forward Port: `8053` (targets the authoritative, not the recursor)
- [ ] From an external network: `nmap -p 53 {{ public_ip }}`
      Expected: open or filtered (not closed)
- [ ] Public delegation test:
      `curl -s "https://dns.google/resolve?name={{ environments.prod.dns_domain }}&type=SOA" | jq .Status`
      Expected: `0` (NOERROR — Google can resolve via your authoritative server)

